Package it.polimi.ingsw.server.model.turnstates

Enum TurnState

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<TurnState>
it.polimi.ingsw.server.model.turnstates.TurnState
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<TurnState>, java.lang.constant.Constable
public enum TurnState
extends java.lang.Enum<TurnState>
The enum containing all the states. All states of the turn are instantiated as values of the enum TurnCreator; for this reason, it is guaranteed the existence of exactly 1 instance for each turn state at runtime.
